dct_title_s: Map of the Strikers Bay Farm : estate of Mrs. Ann Rogers, decd., part of the estate of John Clendining and part of the Herman LeRoy Farm
dct_description_sm: Cadastral map. Also shows names of adjoining landholders, locations of old roads and buildings and original shoreline. Oriented with north to the upper left. Historic Maps copy 1 is hand colored. Historic Maps copy 2 uncolored, not backed with linen. Includes text.
dct_publisher_sm: [New York : City Surveyor : 187-?] ([New York] : Lith. G. Braunlich)
